possibilities for further expanding bilateral ties in defense.
</P>
<P>
Stankevicius said the agreement provides for cooperation in
democratic control over the armed forces and the drafting of
legislation, as well as planning and financing involvement in
international peacekeeping and humanitarian missions and other
spheres. 
