<HEADLINE> Cases of Malaria in Zimbabwe on Decrease </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, September 4 (Xinhua) -- Zimbabwean Health and Child
Welfare Ministry said on Monday that there has been a significant
decrease in malaria cases since January this year when compared
with the same period last year.
</P>
