step for development, the WFP official said, adding that there are
now good programs in this regard in Bangladesh.
</P>
<P>
He said WFP's goal is also to help the government get prepared
for meeting any emergency situation like flood, cyclone and other
natural disasters. Bangladesh has a high degree of efficiency in
the implementation of food assisted programs, he praised.
</P>
<P>
President Shahabuddin thanked Wemer for his keen interest in
the process of supplying food to the poor people and successfully
assisting vulnerable group development and rural development
activities in the country. 
