Association said: "The athletes have trained to their best and we
hope that the hockey team and boxers return with medals."
Pakistan has won 10 Olympic medals, eight in field hockey since
its first appearance in the 1948 London Olympics.
</P>
<P>
Pakistan won gold medals in Rome 1960, Mexico 1968, and Los
Angeles in 1984 and has snatched two silver and two bronze medals
in field hockey.
</P>
