and would like to make all efforts to develop healthy relations
between China and Australia.
</P>
<P>
He said Australia has supported the one-China stance and will
continue to do so.
</P>
<P>
The Australian Guests are visiting China at the invitation of
the Chinese People's Institute of Foreign Affairs. 
