Michael Knight has warned that Sydney's rail system will struggle
to cope during the Olympic Games.
</P>
<P>
"There's obviously a worry about the train system. No matter
how well the transport system works -- even if there are no
derailments, no hold-ups, and every train runs on time -- it will
