<HEADLINE> A Spanish with 6.2 Kilograms of Heroin Arrested in Karachi </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, September 4 (Xinhua) -- The Customs Drug Enforcement
Staff at Karachi International Airport arrested a Spanish national
with 6.2 kilograms of heroin powder in his possession on Sunday
night, police officials said.
</P>
<P>
Leonardo Pomares Moraga was leaving for Paro by Swiss Air
flight SR-389 when stopped by the Customs staff on ground of
suspicion.
</P>
<P>
An examination of his baggage resulted in the recovery of 6.2
kilograms of heroin powder concealed in a bed cover.
</P>
<P>
The accused was arrested and a case registered against him on
charge of drug smuggling. 
</P>
