performances in Santiago and other Chilean cities designed to
celebrate the 30th anniversary of the establishment of Sino-
Chilean diplomatic ties.
</P>
<P>
The troupe arrived here Saturday for a six-day visit to the
Andean nation. After Chile, they will travel to Argentina, Brazil
and Mexico.  
</P>
</TEXT>
