<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Two persons were killed and
10 others including a child injured when a high-intensity
explosion rocked a bus waiting room in Lahore Sunday afternoon,
the Associated Press of Pakistan (APP)quoting police sources
reported.
