Eye witnesses said the deafening explosion was heard in
surrounding areas.
</P>
<P>
The injured were later rushed to the Mayo Hospital.
</P>
<P>
A bomb disposal unit and the local administration people
reached the spot immediately while law enforcement agencies
cordoned off the area.
